'''Amédée Pacôme Nkoulou''' (wavutse 1988) ni umuyobozi wa film muri [[Gabon|Gabon.]]

== Umwuga ==
Nkoulou yakiriye impamyabumenyi ye mu 2007 hanyuma ajya kwiga ibijyanye na sinema ndetse n’amajwi yerekana amashusho muri Institut Supérieur de l'Imashusho et du Son muri [[Wagadugu|Ouagadougou]] . Yagarutse muri Gabon mu 2011 akora akazi ko kwimenyereza umwuga mu mishinga myinshi. <ref name=":0" /> Yabaye umuyobozi wungirije kuri ''L'oeil de la cité ya'' Samantha Biffot (2012), Dialemi ya Nadine ''Otsobogo'' (2013) na ''Sans Famille ya'' Pauline Mvélé (2013).  Muri 2014, filime ya mbere ya Nkoulou, ''Moane Mory'', iminota 20 ngufi, yasohotse nyuma yimyaka ibiri yo kwitegura. Ku nkunga yatanzwe n’ikigo cya leta cya Gabon Igis, iyi filime yerekana inama yabereye mu imurikagurisha ry’ubuhanzi hagati y’umunyeshuri ukiri muto Isa na Jack, umurangi uri mu myaka 40, bikura mu rukundo. ''Moane Mory'' yatoranijwe mu iserukiramuco rya sinema ry’iburayi ryabereye i Libreville no muri firime ngufi mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Cannes 2014 . 

Filime ye ya kabiri, ''Une vie après le bloc'', yasohotse mu 2016. Iyi documentaire isuzuma abaganga babiri bo muri Gabon bashiraho pacemakers na prostateque yivi.  Filime ya mbere ya Nkoulou ngenge yitwa ''Boxe Libreville'', yasohotse muri 2018. Irerekana umusore wifuza guterana amakofe, Christ, igihe yitoza i Libreville hagati y’amatora y’umukuru w’igihugu cya Gaboniya 2016 . ''Umukinnyi w'iteramakofe Libreville'' yinjiye mu marushanwa mpuzamahanga ya Filime ngufi na Hagati muri Vision du Réel .  Yabonye igihembo cya documentaire nziza muri Festival de cine africano de Tarif muri Espagne.  Yerekanwe mu bindi birori byinshi bya firime, harimo Internationales Dokumentarfilmf Festival München  na Ecrans Noirs muri Kameruni. 
